24Jr 9:4 "Beware of your friends; do not trust your brothers. For every brother is a deceiver, and every friend a slanderer.
24Jr 9:5 Friend deceives friend, and no one speaks the truth. They have taught their tongues to lie; they weary themselves with sinning.
