24Jr 11:5 Then I will fulfill the oath I swore to your forefathers, to give them a land flowing with milk and honey'--the land you possess today." I answered, "Amen, LORD."
24Jr 11:6 The LORD said to me, "Proclaim all these words in the towns of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem£º 'Listen to the terms of this covenant and follow them.
24Jr 11:7 From the time I brought your forefathers up from Egypt until today, I warned them again and again, saying, "Obey me."
