24Jr 11:10 They have returned to the sins of their forefathers, who refused to listen to my words. They have followed other gods to serve them. Both the house of Israel and the house of Judah have broken the covenant I made with their forefathers.
24Jr 11:11 Therefore this is what the LORD says£º 'I will bring on them a disaster they cannot escape. Although they cry out to me, I will not listen to them.
