24Jr 11:21 "Therefore this is what the LORD says about the men of Anathoth who are seeking your life and saying, 'Do not prophesy in the name of the LORD or you will die by our hands'--
24Jr 11:22 therefore this is what the LORD Almighty says£º 'I will punish them. Their young men will die by the sword, their sons and daughters by famine.
24Jr 11:23 Not even a remnant will be left to them, because I will bring disaster on the men of Anathoth in the year of their punishment.'"
24Jr 12:1 You are always righteous, O LORD, when I bring a case before you. Yet I would speak with you about your justice£º Why does the way of the wicked prosper? Why do all the faithless live at ease?
