24Jr 32:13 "In their presence I gave Baruch these instructions£º
24Jr 32:14 'This is what the LORD Almighty, the God of Israel, says£º Take these documents, both the sealed and unsealed copies of the deed of purchase, and put them in a clay jar so they will last a long time.
