24Jr 34:1 While Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army and all the kingdoms and peoples in the empire he ruled were fighting against Jerusalem and all its surrounding towns, this word came to Jeremiah from the LORD£º
24Jr 34:2 "This is what the LORD, the God of Israel, says£º Go to Zedekiah king of Judah and tell him, 'This is what the LORD says£º I am about to hand this city over to the king of Babylon, and he will burn it down.
