26Ezk 44:23 They are to teach my people the difference between the holy and the common and show them how to distinguish between the unclean and the clean.
26Ezk 44:24 "'In any dispute, the priests are to serve as judges and decide it according to my ordinances. They are to keep my laws and my decrees for all my appointed feasts, and they are to keep my Sabbaths holy.
