26Ezk 48:29 "This is the land you are to allot as an inheritance to the tribes of Israel, and these will be their portions," declares the Sovereign LORD.
26Ezk 48:30 "These will be the exits of the city£º Beginning on the north side, which is 4,500 cubits long,
